<div class='toload lemma'>
<p><span class='envidentifier'>Lemma 1.4.18</span>
A proper filter $F$ on a Boolean semigroup $S$ is an ultrafilter if and only if it is <em>prime</em>: If $s\lor t\in F$, then $s\in F$ or $t\in F$.
</p>
</div>